    end = 10 ** 10
    mid = (start + end) // 2
    ans = 10 ** 20
    while start <= end:
        sq = mid
        zz = mid * mid
        cb = int(zz ** (1 / 3))
        val = cb + 1
        val = val ** 3
        if val == zz:
            cb += 1
        dif = sq - cb
        if dif >= X:
            ans = min(ans, zz)
            end = mid - 1
            mid = (start + end) // 1
        else:
            start = mid + 1
            mid = (start + end) // 2
    return ans
